00:21:31.020 --> 00:21:33.460 align:middle line:84%
so that they benefit
from it as well.

00:21:33.460 --> 00:21:36.050 align:middle line:84%
I've spoken to a number
of farmers unions.

00:21:36.050 --> 00:21:38.480 align:middle line:90%
And the answers are spectacular.

