It's always, how
quickly can we start?

00:21:45.530 --> 00:21:46.770 align:middle line:90%
When can we start?

00:21:46.770 --> 00:21:48.350 align:middle line:84%
This is how simple
this philosophy

00:21:48.350 --> 00:21:52.230 align:middle line:84%
is because how do we attract
farmers and businesses

00:21:52.230 --> 00:21:53.510 align:middle line:90%
into this model.

00:21:53.510 --> 00:21:56.060 align:middle line:84%
And this is what we
show how inclusive

00:21:56.060 --> 00:21:58.710 align:middle line:84%
this philosophy of Ubuntu
and contributionism

00:21:58.710 --> 00:22:00.880 align:middle line:84%
