in their community

00:22:08.010 --> 00:22:09.650 align:middle line:90%
while it benefits themselves.

00:22:09.650 --> 00:22:13.600 align:middle line:84%
So how will we invite
existing factories

00:22:13.600 --> 00:22:16.730 align:middle line:84%
and existing businesses to
participate in these community

00:22:16.730 --> 00:22:17.530 align:middle line:90%
projects?

00:22:17.530 --> 00:22:18.470 align:middle line:90%
It's very simple.

00:22:18.470 --> 00:22:19.940 align:middle line:90%
I'll give you an example.

00:22:19.940 --> 00:22:23.680 align:middle line:84%
Remember, we set up community
projects of all kinds.

00:22:23.680 --> 00:22:26.340 align:middle line:84%
Anything that you can imagine
can become a community project.

00:22:26.340 --> 00:22:27.300 align:middle line:90%
It's up to us.

00:22:27.300 --> 00:22:29.780 align:middle line:84%
We decide what we're
going to do and set up.

00:22:29.780 --> 00:22:33.350 align:middle line:84%
So if we need to make
bicycle spokes for bicycles,

00:22:33.350 --> 00:22:36.700 align:middle line:84%
