project that works with sand.

00:22:43.230 --> 00:22:47.330 align:middle line:84%
Anything that we want to do, if
we need a research laboratory

00:22:47.330 --> 00:22:51.160 align:middle line:84%
to provide whatever we need for
the scientists that are making

00:22:51.160 --> 00:22:53.740 align:middle line:84%
new materials, we'll set
up the research laboratory

00:22:53.740 --> 00:22:57.425 align:middle line:84%
to provide the components for
new materials that use hemp

00:22:57.425 --> 00:22:59.790 align:middle line:84%
and graphene to create
new materials that

00:22:59.790 --> 00:23:02.900 align:middle line:84%
are far superior than
anything we can imagine.

00:23:02.900 --> 00:23:05.870 align:middle line:84%
Laboratories, research
laboratories, scientists,

00:23:05.870 --> 00:23:09.090 align:middle line:84%
inventors will be invited
to come and set up

00:23:09.090 --> 00:23:11.120 align:middle line:84%
whatever research
facilities they need.

00:23:11.120 --> 00:23:13.037 align:middle line:84%
And everything they need
will be provided for.

00:23:13.037 --> 00:23:13.836 align:middle line:90%
Why?

00:23:13.836 --> 00:23:14.670 align:middle line:90%
Because we can.

00:23:14.670 --> 00:23:16.700 align:middle line:90%
And we choose to do so.

00:23:16.700 --> 00:23:20.170 align:middle line:84%
People that develop cures
for all disease, doctors,

00:23:20.170 --> 00:23:22.800 align:middle line:84%
scientists, inventors that
work in the healing industry

00:23:22.800 --> 00:23:26.090 align:middle line:84%
will be invited to work in
our hospital and our research

00:23:26.090 --> 00:23:29.350 align:middle line:84%
facilities to provide
the cure for all disease.

00:23:29.350 --> 00:23:31.580 align:middle line:84%
Everything becomes
possible as long

00:23:31.580 --> 00:23:35.300 align:middle line:84%
as we do this cooperatively
and collaboratively.

00:23:35.300 --> 00:23:37.800 align:middle line:90%
So here is an example.

00:23:37.800 --> 00:23:39.835 align:middle line:84%
In our town, we
have a wood factory.

00:23:39.835 --> 00:23:42.460 align:middle line:84%
Well, how will they benefit
from-- why should I join you?

00:23:42.460 --> 00:23:43.989 align:middle line:84%
And say, well,
what's in it for me?

00:23:43.989 --> 00:23:45.530 align:middle line:84%
Well, the following
is in it for you.

00:23:45.530 --> 00:23:46.946 align:middle line:84%
If you make your
wood factory that

00:23:46.946 --> 00:23:51.060 align:middle line:84%
makes window frames and
door frames, wooden door

00:23:51.060 --> 00:23:54.020 align:middle line:84%
frames and windows, if
you make your business

00:23:54.020 --> 00:23:55.690 align:middle line:84%
part of the community
project, you

00:23:55.690 --> 00:23:59.300 align:middle line:84%
get the following-- free
electricity, no rates and taxes

00:23:59.300 --> 00:24:01.190 align:middle line:84%
because remember,
the town belongs us.

00:24:01.190 --> 00:24:04.380 align:middle line:84%
Why should we pay rates
and taxes to ourselves?

00:24:04.380 --> 00:24:07.070 align:middle line:84%
You get free labor from the
people that come and work

00:24:07.070 --> 00:24:09.060 align:middle line:90%
in your community project now.

00:24:09.060 --> 00:24:10.350 align:middle line:90%
You get free components.

00:24:10.350 --> 00:24:12.140 align:middle line:84%
The wood will come
from our wood factory,

00:24:12.140 --> 00:24:13.590 align:middle line:90%
which is a community project.

00:24:13.590 --> 00:24:16.040 align:middle line:84%
The glue will come from
our laboratory, scientists

00:24:16.040 --> 00:24:17.800 align:middle line:84%
that are making glues
that are much better

00:24:17.800 --> 00:24:20.200 align:middle line:90%
and biodegradable and nontoxic.

00:24:20.200 --> 00:24:23.190 align:middle line:84%
So basically, you'll be
getting all your components

00:24:23.190 --> 00:24:24.980 align:middle line:90%
to make windows and doors.

00:24:24.980 --> 00:24:31.070 align:middle line:84%
And in return, you retain 1/3 of
the profits made from this wood

00:24:31.070 --> 00:24:33.870 align:middle line:84%
factory because it's
now a community project.

00:24:33.870 --> 00:24:36.140 align:middle line:84%
The other 2/3 go
to the community

00:24:36.140 --> 00:24:39.770 align:middle line:84%
to benefit the community and
bring money into the community

00:24:39.770 --> 00:24:43.410 align:middle line:84%
coffers, while we still
operate under a financial

00:24:43.410 --> 00:24:45.360 align:middle line:90%
and a capitalist system.

00:24:45.360 --> 00:24:49.580 align:middle line:84%
So you, as the owner of the
factory or any other business,

00:24:49.580 --> 00:24:53.140 align:middle line:84%
